{"tid":2097430,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我想學整一件機器出嚟","createTime":"2020-07-06T23:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T12:42:12.000Z","uid":63626,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0760e2d8dfeadc7795dcfdee00492929938020bd","tid":2097430,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"應該由咩知識開始入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />物理？<br />\n我指係一啲簡單嘅機械， 例如一個定時放啲水出嚟比狗飲嘅機器？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我對呢方面無乜認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知上述嘅機器算唔算簡單<br />\n或者再簡單啲，先學整一個識不停禁制嘅假手<br />\n<br />\n如果我係當興趣自學，應該從邊方面入手/需要用到邊方面嘅知識？<br />\n利申：不是理科出生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110c2e2c314aca5c88d54f9588ad6f4f1dfb491f","tid":2097430,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:30:43.000Z","msg":"學computing engineering"},{"pid":"8e72d4c937686e7f3b02a870ec2988480a9388c4","tid":2097430,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110c2e2c314aca5c88d54f9588ad6f4f1dfb491f","tid":2097430,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:30:43.000Z","msg":"學computing engineering"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"簡單既學電子"},{"pid":"f86cf4bc1cc8bb44f9a32b6d8ee5ed636db1606b","tid":2097430,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:31:21.000Z","msg":"買d 描述Arduino板睇下書自己都整倒，唔難"},{"pid":"adf16fe68f7089a90d9337260bd298b001bbe9b0","tid":2097430,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"如果你真係白紙一張<br />\n建議你上網搵想要嘅野跟住diy<br />\n當你做多幾次就研究埋當中原理<br />\n最後就睇你嘅天份<br />\n識唔識得融會貫通自己諗個design"},{"pid":"eadaed175b3e1191e0dc1bf86de25c2348885b7c","tid":2097430,"uid":168762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"搵個簡單概目標機械 上網跟住人做 <br 